thread.title: Agon Hawk
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Agon Hawk

author: Agon Hawk
title: Agon Hawk
text:
Why is it that it costs more doing it online than bringing your packing to send it in the shop?!
Shop service assistant was very helpful and offered great service however the prices were significantly higher doing it in the shop.
I ended up just doing it online on my phone and then brought it in to the shop to ship it... Should be priced the same doing it in the shop!
Otherwise, excellent service, and if it was the same price in shop and online, I'd give 5 stars :)
